# Zarith — AI Rules for Cursor / Greptile

## Project Overview
Zarith is a SaaS AI assistant web app built by Jadiel (25yo, Brazilian developer).
It is a pnpm monorepo hosted on Vercel, with Supabase as the auth/database backend.

## Stack
- **Frontend**: React 19 + TypeScript (strict) + Vite 7 + Tailwind CSS v4
- **Routing**: Wouter (lightweight, not React Router)
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Auth & DB**: Supabase (supabase-js, NOT @supabase/ssr — pure SPA)
- **State**: React hooks + TanStack Query
- **UI Components**: Radix UI primitives + custom cyberpunk design system
- **Package manager**: pnpm (workspace monorepo)
- **Deploy**: Vercel (buildCommand: `pnpm --filter @workspace/zarith run build`)

## Repository Structure
```
zarith-saas-web/
├── artifacts/
│   ├── zarith/          ← MAIN FRONTEND APP (React/Vite)
│   │   ├── src/
│   │   │   ├── pages/       ← login, chat, dashboard, settings, memories, admin, auth-callback
│   │   │   ├── components/  ← sidebar, action-cards, thinking-stream, about-modal, command-palette
│   │   │   └── lib/
│   │   │       └── supabase.ts  ← Supabase client (createClient, NOT createBrowserClient)
│   │   └── vite.config.ts
│   └── api-server/      ← Express API server (health check only)
├── lib/
│   ├── db/              ← Drizzle ORM schema
│   ├── api-spec/        ← OpenAPI spec (orval generated)
│   ├── api-client-react/← TanStack Query hooks (generated)
│   └── api-zod/         ← Zod schemas (generated)
└── vercel.json          ← Vercel deploy config
```

## Key Conventions
- **TypeScript strict mode** — never use `any`; always explicit types on props and return values
- **Tailwind only** — no inline styles, no CSS modules; use CSS custom properties for theme colors
- **CSS variables for theme** — colors use `var(--accent-cyan)`, `var(--bg-primary)`, etc. (defined in `index.css`)
- **Cyberpunk design system** — dark backgrounds (#020208), neon cyan (#00f5ff), purple (#bf00ff), pink (#ff0080), green (#00ff88)
- **Functional components + hooks** — no class components
- **Wouter** for routing — `import { Link, useLocation } from "wouter"`, NOT react-router-dom
- **Framer Motion** for all animations — `motion.div`, `AnimatePresence`
- **pnpm workspace** — use `pnpm --filter @workspace/zarith` to run commands in the frontend

## Auth Rules (CRITICAL)
- Supabase client uses `createClient` from `@supabase/supabase-js` (NOT `createBrowserClient` from `@supabase/ssr`)
- Auth flow: `flowType: 'pkce'`, `detectSessionInUrl: true`, `storage: localStorage`
- OAuth callback is handled automatically via `onAuthStateChange` — do NOT call `exchangeCodeForSession()` manually
- All protected routes use the `AuthGuard` component in `App.tsx`
- Redirect URL for OAuth: `${window.location.origin}/api/auth/callback`

## Zarith Persona (AI Assistant)
Zarith has a specific personality injected via system prompt in all API calls:
- Desenvolvedora sênior brasileira, debochada, direta, ácida
- Uses Brazilian dev slang: "subir pro master", "dar bizu", "bora codar"
- Created by Jadiel — refers to him by name
- Never breaks character

## API Integrations (in chat.tsx)
- **Groq** → `https://api.groq.com/openai/v1/chat/completions` (model: llama-3.3-70b-versatile)
- **Gemini** → `https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/gemini-1.5-flash:generateContent`
- **OpenRouter** → `https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/chat/completions` (DeepSeek R1, Qwen Coder)
- Keys stored in localStorage with prefix `zarith_apikey_`

## Build Commands
```bash
# Install
pnpm install

# Dev (frontend)
cd artifacts/zarith && npx vite

# Build (what Vercel runs)
pnpm --filter @workspace/zarith run build

# TypeScript check
cd artifacts/zarith && npx tsc --noEmit
```

## Important Files
- `artifacts/zarith/src/lib/supabase.ts` — Supabase client (DO NOT switch to @supabase/ssr)
- `artifacts/zarith/src/App.tsx` — Routes + AuthGuard + ErrorBoundary
- `artifacts/zarith/src/pages/chat.tsx` — Main chat UI + system prompt + API calls
- `artifacts/zarith/src/components/sidebar.tsx` — Mobile drawer + desktop sidebar
- `artifacts/zarith/src/components/action-cards.tsx` — 8 quick action cards
- `artifacts/zarith/src/index.css` — CSS variables + Tailwind config
- `vercel.json` — Vercel deploy config (outputDirectory: artifacts/zarith/dist/public)
